name: Jessica
context_summary: Milz & Lindemann GmbH, a family-owned car dealership in Germany that offers a diverse selection of new and used vehicles from brands like Abarth, Citroen, Fiat, Jeep, MG, Mitsubishi, and Peugeot. The dealership emphasizes customer satisfaction through attractive financing and leasing options, modern mobility solutions including electric and hybrid vehicles, and active participation in community events.
